/strong></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>25篇搞笑故事和GoI格式。基本是独立故事与基金会宇宙中的自收容故事。</p> <p><strong>1.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/everyone-knows">人尽皆知</a> by Bryx</p> <blockquote> <p>每个同行组织，主要和次要的。每个异常人员。O5将它们输入计算机，并等待它输出一份名单。所有人的名字都在上面，无一例外。</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>2.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-most-dangerous-game-of-all">最可怕的游戏</a> by Dmatix</p> <blockquote> <p>他不管自己根本不知道她去了哪里，也不管她远比自己聪明，敏捷和强壮。他一定要找到她，然后杀掉她，无论她跑到天涯海角。</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>3.</strong> <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/joey-fucknuts-builds-a-flying-machine">joey-fucknuts-builds-a-flying-machine</a> by CadaverCommander</p> <blockquote> <p>The woman was wearing what Joey thought was a very cute yellow sundress and carried an umbrella with a small flamethrower installed in it, which, she had explained to Joey previously, was supposed to burn the rain before it could make her wet. Joey thought that was pretty smart.</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>4.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/grant-request-for-a-replacement-keyboard-because-the-caps-lo">批准获得替代键盘的申请因为现在这个的大写锁定坏了</a></p> <blockquote> <p>RU CI ZAI SHE HUI JIE GOU SHANG DE BENG KUI BU NENG BEI RONG REN。PU LUO MI XIU SI SHI YAN SHI YI YONG BAO CHUANG XIN WEI AO，DAN TA DE YUAN GONG QUE YAO WEI LIE ZHI ER ANG GUI DE JI SHU SHOU KU。</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>5.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/where-they-all-go">它们的去向</a> by Salman Corbette</p> <blockquote> <p>基金会发射了空间望远镜23阿尔法，以求对此物体进行直接观测。</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><strong>6.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/ooo-ooo-ooo-o