by djkaktus</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>他发现了怪物。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>人类属于一种非常特殊的非反常生命形式。类人异常可能看起来像是人类，但只是“类人”。因此，他们无权享有道德委员会给予人类的权利和特权。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>4. Dr. Asma Tareen | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2669">SCP-2669</a>: &quot;怯薛1号&quot;</strong> by kalinin</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>一颗可悲的流星。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>我要用你的恐惧包裹自己。培植它、把它融进我自己。现在已经有很多了，再多加点还能少痛苦一会儿。我完全有理由耐心等待。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>5. CONTROLLER与 PLANTER | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3721">SCP-3721</a>: &quot;过时武器系统&quot;</strong> by UraniumEmpire</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>死亡战争的腐朽残余。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>CONTROLLER:</strong> 就位。<br /> <em><strong>PLANTER</strong> 开火。</em></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>6. &quot;M&quot;/&quot;鬼魂&quot; | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3625">SCP-3625</a>: &quot;无情的美利坚表情包机器&quot;</strong> by djkaktus</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A misanthropic nobody.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>请记得我，　　　　　　　　<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-95147-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >7</a></sup>，全能的上帝会用他那公正的右手保佑我。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>7. olliefox | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3312">SCP-3312</a>: &quot;OwO这是啥米？&quot;</strong> by Dog Teeth</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>你妈妈警告过兽迷的。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Thotticusprime:</strong> 你知道他快破产了对吧<br /> <strong>olliefox:</strong> 对但也不是那么坏因为<br /> <strong>olliefox:</strong> 他大概会试图去穿着它们工作或者干别的哈哈哈<br /> <strong>olliefox:</strong> 他要去做啥带着兽装杀人吗？？</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>8. Drs. Jean Durand 与Mátyás Nemeş | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-186">SCP-186</a>: &quot;为了终结一切战争&quot;</strong> by kalinin</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>夸张的现代战争的恐怖</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>我们不再是军队了。不再是，我们是动物，一起被困在这森林里，完全没有方向。有时，当Volikov睡着了，我听见法国人在树林里，和匈牙利人叫喊，又叫又笑。我宁愿去听Volikov的惨叫。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>9. 歪歪扭扭的男人 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-783">SCP-783</a>: &quot;那里有个歪歪扭扭的人&quot;</strong> by Shaggydredlocks</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>一个入侵的虐待狂。</em></span><br /></p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p>那儿住了个歪歪扭扭的男人，干着些偷偷摸摸的勾当<br /> 他拿着个破破烂烂的笼子，拄着个弯弯曲曲的拐杖<br /> 他偷了个瘦瘦小小的孩子，长长短短的尖叫回荡在路旁<br /> 而那个歪歪扭扭的小家伙最后被砸碎在了轮子上</p> </blockquote> </div> <p><span class="h2"><strong>10. 昏厥交响曲 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4833">SCP-4833</a>: &quot;昏厥交响曲&quot;</strong> by Tufto</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>高中糟透了。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-4833曾在异常事务中扮演重要角色，自20世纪40年代晚期起在异常地下世界因绑架和对大量人员进行强迫改造而格外受人畏惧。</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>11. vector | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-353">SCP-353</a>: “病媒”</strong> by Pair of Ducks</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>一个毫无歉意的超级恶棍。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>至今，对象真实身份不明，因为对象仅将自己称为“Vector”（“病媒”），并拒绝回答有关其过去的问题。 SCP-353称其移至西方世界是为了寻找更多的疾病，将它们加入其“收藏”中。当被问及原因时，对象除“因为我可以。”以外不作任何回答。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>12. Dr. Madison Craggs | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3033">SCP-3033</a>: &quot;人形武器&quot;</strong> by Lazar Lyusternik</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>冷战的寒冷产物。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>嗯……你应该知道这些吧。在美国当健全的员工，然后叛逃到苏联。之后苏联解体。那我们这些研究生物武器的人还能在哪找份有意义的工作？</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>13. 狄瓦族 | <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/scp-140">SCP-140</a>: &quot;未完编年史&quot;</strong> by AssertiveRoland</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>我们暴虐的先锋。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>我必须知道。很抱歉。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>14. 乔纳森•巴克 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1832">SCP-1832</a>: &quot;伪信念治疗师&quot;</strong> by Gaffsey</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>需要感觉特殊的人。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>我有这力量。治愈别人或者袖手旁观，审判邪恶，在一个人最需要爱和怜悯时拒绝他。这种感觉就像成为了上帝。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>15. Dennis Huang | <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4504">SCP-4504</a>: &quot;The Handless Man&quot;</strong> by wmaitla</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A normal man that had a very bad decade.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Dr White:</strong> Yes, yes, I’ve heard it before. Now Dennis-<br /> <strong>SCP-4504:</strong> 4504.</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>16. Pentagram | <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4406">SCP-4406</a>: &quot;SUDDEN THUNDER&quot;</strong> by aismallard and pxdnbluesoul</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>Never trust the CIA.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>The government confirmed the existence of SCP-4406, but resisted requests for technical information on the anomaly's capabilities or design.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>17.罗伯特•蒙托克博士 | <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/tuftos-proposal">Tufto的提案</a>: &quot;深红之王&quot;</strong> by Tufto</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A Nietzschean Übermensch.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>我知道何为善，何为恶，我在他们之中看不到两者任一。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>18. Randolph T. Metzger | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-748">SCP-748</a>: &quot;工业解体&quot;</strong> by Metaphysician</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>一路上都是齿轮。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>工厂服从我的意愿。工人们受我摆布。我是这里的神。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>19. Samuel Decard | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-2701">SCP-2701</a>: &quot;真正的孤立&quot;</strong> by Mortte</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>一个被过分逼迫的父亲。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>我看着他的眼睛，我看到一个选择成为野兽的人。我想要他烂在我能找到的最深，最黑的洞里。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>20. Kumiho | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-953">SCP-953</a>: &quot;多形态类人&quot;</strong> by DrClef</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>了解你的民间传说。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>任何一次让她注意到的目视，她都会想要进行报复。把她像只动物那样关起来……当她出来，她会出来，她会杀了所有看见她的人。她不会为任何东西安定下来。</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>21. 圣诞魔人 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4666">SCP-4666</a>: &quot;圣诞魔人&quot;</strong> by Hercules Rockefeller</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>克朗普斯。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>你不做玩具，就没得吃。不要停止做玩具，不要睡着。不然他会伤害你。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>22. Josep Oriol/&quot;Enigma&quot; | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3512">SCP-3512</a>: &quot;知道的越多&quot;</strong> by psul</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>抓住艺术品小偷。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>你要做的第一件事就是不要把性感女人当女人看待。准确地说，不要再把他们当成人了。把它们想象成乐器——在你演奏它们之前，你需要知道如何调整它们。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>23. SCP-3333-1 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3333">SCP-3333</a>: &quot;妖塔&quot;</strong> by Jekeled</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>他们和你想的不一样。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>当然，我对他们都不太了解，所以如果有什么不对，我该怎么说呢……</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>24.蒂姆•艾伦 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4844">SCP-4844</a>: &quot;最后的男人&quot;</strong> by TyGently</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>宋飞隐藏的对手。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-4844能进行多种技艺，包括飞行、自发显现及消失、操控物体和物质、脱口秀等。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>25. 基金会 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djkaktus-s-proposal-iii">djkaktus提案III</a>: &quot;终结的方式&quot;</strong> by djkaktus</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>一台太大的机器。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;世间无正亦无邪&quot;</p> </blockquote> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-2" style="display:none"> <p><span class="h2"><strong>1. Dr. Bright | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/unfinished-business">未竟的事业</a></strong> by TroyL</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>有着未竟事业的人。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>‘这只是一次小小的挫折，Alto，’Jack心想。‘只是一次小小的挫折。’</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>2. SCP-1915 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-stars-do-not-wait-for-you">群星不待</a></strong> by Dmatix</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>空无。</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>现实不可承载空无，他们总这么说，但缺失之物对现实的关怀可谓微不足道。</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>3. Pico Wilson | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-cool-war-hub">Cool之战</a> - (系列)</strong> by Randomini</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>Just like daddy.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>“你就像一只关在笼子里的鸟儿，不过笼子是使用玻璃做出来的而且你是头犀牛。你都没意识到你能够摆脱束缚，对吧？”</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>4. Thoth | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/bird">Team Bird</a> - (Series)</strong> by not_a_seagull/Lt Flops/Ayers/Quantum Physician</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A vengeful god.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>To which Thoth replied, <em>to reject my wisdom is to spite me. Yes, to be in absence of my wisdom for too long is a blasphemous offence. But to anger me, truly, it would take the effort of one who is quite mad</em>.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>5. Alto Clef Jr. | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/goc-act-hub">GOC ACT</a> - (Series)</strong> by DolphinSlugchugger</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>An ending behind the barrel of a gun.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;I can call what I'm about to do to you revenge but it doesn't change the fact that I'm getting off on this shit, that I'm doing it for my own sense of karma.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>6. SCP-3125 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/antimemetics-division-hub">There Is No Antimemetics Division</a> - (Series)</strong> by qntm</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The ultimate nemesis of the Antimemetics Division.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Destroying all knowledge of it was the only way to destroy it. And restoring my memories was a foolproof way to bring it back!&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>7. Harold Maine | <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/at-the-library">Televono Telefex Secrecy-8</a> - (Series)</strong> by Wils</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A slimy, sadistic coward.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>He looked up, suddenly remembering the woman and child standing before him. He regarded them intently and counted up to five in his head before responding. He'd read somewhere how that made people feel uncomfortable.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>8. Natasha Tokyopop | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/speed-demon-hub">Speed Demon</a> - (Series)</strong> by A Random Day</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A jilted lover, left literally heartbroken.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;Me, right now? Everything I've done in the past five years? All you, Ruku.&quot;<br /> The glass disintegrates. The drones begin to pour in.<br /> &quot;All. Your. Fault.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>9. Cousin Johnny | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-oct-hub">The OCT</a> - (Kinch's Entries)</strong> by Kinchtheknifeblade</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The herald of a new age for Christianity.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>The priest, the father, the skinny little man with the white collar and the whiter hair, combed up and toward the side like it hid the fact that he was balding. Johnny wished, quite dearly, that he could reach out and touch it. Rip them out from the core. Tear them out as he screams. Make him say thank you. Make him love him and force the hair down his throat, have the old piece of shit fooling no one devour the remnants of what was never close to a lustrous mane.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>10. D-7294 | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wriggle-like-a-fucking-eel">Wriggle Like a Fucking Eel</a></strong> by Decibelles</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>Serial killers are rarely &quot;insane&quot;.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;You can't even serve the one purpose you were made for, can you. Do you feel anything?&quot; No response except for the same sounds. &quot;What will change?&quot; He broke off a finger.</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>11. Skippy | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/your-very-first-scp">Your Very First SCP!</a></strong> by The Great Hippo</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>He only wants to help.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>But yeah, like I was saying — sorry about that, friend. It's just so irritating when people can't follow the format, you know?</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>12. Mr. Redd | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-redd">SCP-REDD</a></strong> by TwistedGears</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>Production stopped for a reason.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>Redd smiled. &quot;Please, no need for the 'Mister' formality. We're all friends here. I'm Redd open parenthesis discontinued closed parenthesis. My friends just call me Redd. How are you, Four?&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>13. The Pit Sloth | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/rise-of-the-pit-sloth-hub">Black Autumn II: Rise of the Pit Sloth</a> - (Series)</strong> by Ihp</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A movie monster, brought to life.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>All she saw was a pair of claws, scraping against the ground, like a pair of keratinous legs sliding on the tile.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>14. Dr. Gregory Greene | <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/ii-tab-po-c-h20-qhs-prn-pain">ii tab po c h2o qhs prn pain</a></strong> by Veiedhimaedhr</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The doctor who conquered immortality.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;If I'm leading you along, then all you lose is time, a null concept now. But if I'm not… I'll make your New Year's resolution really something to remember.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>15. Mr. Night | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/black-as-night">Black as Night</a> - (Series)</strong> by stormbreath</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The Spirit's backbone.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>Mr. Night is one of the top men of the Spirit. He's an old friend of Richard Chappell, and has been in the business with him even longer than I have. Back when Chicago Spirit was the name of a bar, even. Before, too, I think.</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>16. SCP-106 | <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/until-death">Until Death</a></strong> by psul</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>He has all the time in the world.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>Above a ruined throat, she saw a too-wide mouth locked in a rictus grin, and eyes - oh god, those eyes. The thing emerging from the wall before her looked like a man, but its eyes were grey and flat as a shark's.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>17. hatbot.aic | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/hello-world">Hello World</a> - (Series)</strong> by LurkD</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>A child of the Information Age.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>Wikipedia pages. LinkedIn updates. Tumblr posts. Terms and conditions on a media player. An anti-virus scan log. These are some of the things I have to process. Have to learn. All of that noise. Noise. Noise. Noisy fucking primates.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>18. SAPPHIRE | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/non-prophet-organization-hub">A Non-Prophet Organization</a> - (Series)</strong> by Uncle Nicolini/NatVoltaic/Lt Flops/sepiafishie</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>Irrational forces of rationality.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p><em>There is the sun and it is nuclear and it is nothing more.</em></p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>19. Vincent Anderson | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-elusive-anderson">The Elusive Anderson</a> - (Series)</strong> by Jacob Conwell</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The mysterious CEO of Anderson Robotics.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>“Well, uh, I’m not going to kill you, if that’s what you think,” Anderson replied with a chuckle, “You guys all seem to think I’m some kind of James Bond villain when I’m just a small business owner. To be honest, I was hoping to avoid a confrontation like this entirely. You, uh, just came back too early.”</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>20. The Freezer | <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/it-smells-cold">It Smells Cold</a></strong> by Ihp</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>We don't go there.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>For a third… the smell of cold I talked about? Even opening the freezer from the customer side, it reeks of that. I actually had to check that my nose wasn't bleeding after I bought ice cream from the freezer there.</p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p><span class="h2"><strong>21. Mr. Stripes | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/tales-of-mr-collector">Tales of Mr. Collector</a> - (Series)</strong> by Salman Corbette + Guests</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>Wondertainment's little janitor.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>I have very long legs. Very long. Long enough to stretch over a canyon, when I want them to. When I need them to. And long fingers as well. The fingers of a pianist, or a strangler. Long and slender. Made for choking. Not a pianist.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>22. Dr. Glut | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/a-man-at-the-top-of-his-profession">A Man At the Top of His Profession</a></strong> by name</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>Everything is perfectly fine.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>&quot;No, you saw nothing.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>23. Iris Dark | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-dark-web-dke79-o2rg5-4jlw6">'The Dark Web' (DKE79/O2RG5/4JLW6)</a></strong> by DrChandra</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The bottom line is the profit margin.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>It really goes to show that good ethics is good business.</p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>24. The Stairwell | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/six-little-mice">Six Little Mice</a></strong> by Pig_catapult</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The only winning move is not to play.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p><em>There was no escape from the big bad cat</em></p> </blockquote> <p><span class="h2"><strong>25. Elder Foreman Steve Al'uth | <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/recruitment-drive-28126">Recruitment Drive (R-28126)</a></strong> by MayD</span><br /> <span class="h4"><em>The gaping maw of corporate fascism.</em></span></p> <blockquote> <p>Staff reminder: Elder Foremen dislike their existence being acknowledged. Doing so may put your employment at risk. Do not risk your employment.</p> </blockquote> </div> </div> </div> <h1><span>Heartwarming</span></h1> <p>For those who want some wholesomeness.</p> <div id="wiki-tabview-c4c68690023da36460f0bdad9d43486b" class="yui-navset"> <ul class="yui-nav"> <li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>Sirslash47's Selects</em></a></li> </ul> <div class="yui-content"> <div id="wiki-tab-0-0"> <p><strong>1-25</strong></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><strong>1.</strong> <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5270">SCP-5270</a> &quot;Press X to Bear&quot; by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gerrymanderbassist" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2346106&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245625" alt="GerrymanderBassist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2346106)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gerrymanderbassist" >GerrymanderBassist</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/penguin6" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4857652&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245625" alt="Penguin6" style="background-image:url(http://www