					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="display:none"><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/styleFrame.html?.side-block%20.heading%7Bcolor%3A%23ededed%3Bfont-family%3A'%E9%BB%91%E4%BD%93'%2Csans-serif%3Bfont-size%3A0.94rem%3Bborder-bottom%3Asolid%201px%20%23ededed%3B%7D.side-block%7Bborder%3Atransparent%3Bborder-radius%3A0%3Bbox-shadow%3Anone%3Bbackground-color%3A%2321252e%3B%7D.side-block%20.menu-item%20%3E%20.image%7Bdisplay%3Anone%3B%7D.side-block%20div.menu-item%20a%7Bcolor%3A%231eb5e8%3Btransition%3Acolor%200.15s%20linear%3B%7D.side-block%20div.menu-item%20a%3Ahover%7Bcolor%3A%23ffffff%3Btext-decoration%3Anone%3Bbackground-color%3A%231eb5e8%3B%7D" name="styleFrame"></iframe></div> <blockquote> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span><strong>&#187; 这是<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smith-sister-con" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4381648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245628" alt="Smith_sister-con" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4381648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smith-sister-con" >Smith_sister-con</a></span>的记事本 &#171;</strong></span></h2> <h3><span>欢迎，随意翻阅。</span></h3> </div> </blockquote> <div id="wiki-tabview-983645c36ba5a233aaa80972950c6664" class="yui-navset"> <ul class="yui-nav"> <li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>引</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>镜中虚像</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>午间逸话</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>往昔之风</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>此地之外</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>离别赠言</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>本月计分板</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>结语</em></a></li> </ul> <div class="yui-content"> <div id="wiki-tab-0-0"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--files/smith-sister-con-s-personnel-file/Iserlohn" alt="Iserlohn" class="image" /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span class="ruby">这夜里，我在一片空虚中渐行渐远。<span class="rt">Far across the emptiness I walk the night.</span></span></p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">And&nbsp;&nbsp;then？</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><span class="ruby">远离你与我所相守的世界，那里蔚蓝大海倒流入苍穹<span class="rt">Far from the world of you and I,where ocean is bleeding to the sky.</span></span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none"> <blockquote> <p><strong>姓名：</strong><span class="ruby">许晓雨<span class="rt">Gypsophila</span></span></p> <p><strong>安保权限：</strong>3级权限</p> <p><strong>职务：</strong>Mobile-Site-CN研究员，Site-CN-06客座研究员，Area-CN-07客座研究员，<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Gardenia和Auroria的老公</span></p> <p><strong>常驻站点：</strong>Mobile-Site-CN，Site-CN-06</p> <p><strong>简介：</strong>女性，蒙古利亚人种，170cm/48kg。于Mobile-Site-CN与Site-CN-06两站点间定期往来，负责文件转接和少数研究项目等工作。灰发蓝瞳，性格温和，较为可靠。</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">星光四散在你我之间。</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Stardust&nbsp;in&nbsp;you&nbsp;and&nbsp;me.</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>许晓雨出生于江苏南通市，前20年生活正常，18岁时考入西南交通大学材料系，后进入细分专业无机高分子进行深造。</p> <p>大二暑假受到SCP-CN-740影响，被届时临近的研究员Gardenia察觉并及时进行了心理治疗。并被其介绍入基金会，签订保密协议后返回本校学习，按照正常流程毕业后入职基金会并继续攻读研究生学位。</p> <p>入职后负责工作多为文书工作，仅在部分项目的研究涉及所学时会有所参与。由于工作需常在站点间走动，许晓雨被分配至Mobile-Site-CN工作，与研究员Gardenia同宿舍。</p> <p>安静，温和；虽然不算沉默寡言，但确实不怎么说话，仅在少数几个朋友面前才会变得相对开朗与活泼。</p> <p>对薄荷糖与黑巧克力十分喜爱，随身携带至少三包。尽管每日摄入热量严重超标，但奇怪的是她的身材依旧保持在一个较为苗条的水平。</p> <p>爱好方面，对于除羽毛球以外的一切运动都不感兴趣。休息时间更多为猫在宿舍看书或电视剧，偶尔能看到其与Gardenia出门购物，或大或小的毛绒玩具每次必定出现在两人购物袋中。</p> <p>由于对天体有着莫名的强烈兴趣，许晓雨很快与Site-CN-06的研究员Auroria熟识，空闲时经常二人外出观星。</p> <p>感情方面并无任何记录。</p> </div> </div> </div> </blockquote> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-2" style="display:none"> <table class="heritage"> <tr> <td class="title">我的历程</td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>起于他人之口。</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/progress">进步</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2019-02-19</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>Creepypasta</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>“我发明了一种用噩梦做燃料的汽车。这确实很有趣。”</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/secure-facility-dossier-research-site-45">研究性安保设施Site-45</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2019-12-31</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>研究性安保设施Site-45</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>“<strong>官方名称：</strong>SCP基金会西澳大利亚近海研究设施”</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1855">SCP-1855</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2020-02-04</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>旧道路</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>“SCP-1855为一位于路易斯安那州文森特港附近一条小路尽头的区域。”</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-1917">SCP-1917</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2020-02-17</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>工业启示</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>“金属确实很好，但我也想在玻璃取代我的眼睛前看看这个世界。”</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-5588">SCP-5588</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2020-03-27</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>被俘之星依旧闪亮</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>“基金会对该区域的扫描结果显示出一个比任何SCP-5588与包含它们的星系大得多的根部。”</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-5984">SCP-5984</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2020-07-13</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>WAN终将站起</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>“ SCP-5984为一个高6.5米的可动机器人，外形类似于派拉蒙影业《变形金刚》改编电影中的擎天柱。”</p> </div> </td> </tr> </table> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-3" style="display:none"> <table class="heritage"> <tr> <td class="title">我的历程</td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>源于自身所见。</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/gohome">公款旅游：回家</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2019-02-19</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>公款旅游</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>“新年快乐”</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/imissyou">伊人已逝</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2019-03-21</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>She is gone.</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>都过去了。</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/smith-sister-con-s-personnel-file">Smith-sister-con的工作台</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2020-03-27</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>我的作者页</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>嘛，稍微庆祝一下也不是不可以对吧。</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:lighthouse">灯塔</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2020-12-13</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>柏勒洛斯</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>她可以沉入水中。</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:starlost">失星</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2020-12-14</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>斯特罗</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>星河随着梦想消失。</p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:shadow">阴影</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>登记时间：<strong>2021-01-03</strong></p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>柏勒洛斯</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p>她只与自己做伴。</p> </div> </td> </tr> </table> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-4" style="display:none"> <h2><span>尚未经历之事</span></h2> <h3><span>余烬</span></h3> <ul> <li><em>“有趣的是，无论何种文明，只要进步的路上有对火的利用，那么他们在面对未知时的第一个反应便是烧毁。”——《炉火旁静坐的身影》</em></li> </ul> <h3><span>塔尖</span></h3> <ul> <li><em>她在塔尖起舞，风与光鼓掌欢呼。——《晨》</em></li> </ul> <h3><span>《对牧歌时代个世界类似神话的整理与分析》</span></h3> <ul> <li><em>“三子于‘锚’处分离，重逢之日难以望见。”——《“锚”》</em></li> </ul> <ul> <li><a href="http://scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/smith-sister-con">Dia-Er-00</a></li> <li><a href="http://scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/smith-sister-con-2">Dat-Uni-Bas</a></li> <li><a href="http://scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/collab:smith-sister-con">Doc-Ob-07</a></li> <li><a href="http://scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/collab:smiths-translate">Cop-Sto-XX</a></li> </ul> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-5" style="display:none"> <blockquote> <p>Coloress green ideas sleep furiously.<br /></p> <div style="text-align: right;"> <p>——Iserlohn</p> </div> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><em>I’ve seen things you people wouldn’t believe.</em><br /> <em>我所见过的事物,你们人类绝对无法置信</em><br /> <em>Attack ships on fire off the shoulder of Orion.</em><br /> <em>我曾目睹战舰在猎户座端沿起火燃烧</em><br /> <em>I watched c-beams glitter in the dark near the Tanhauser Gate.</em><br /> <em>我看着c射线在唐怀瑟之门附近的黑暗中闪耀</em><br /> <em>All those&#8230;moments will be lost&#8230;in time.</em><br /> <em>所有这些时刻&#8230;终将凐灭在时光的洪流中&#8230;</em><br /> <em>Like&#8230;tears&#8230;in rain.</em><br /> <em>一如眼泪&#8230;消失在雨中&#8230;</em><br /> <em>Time&#8230;to die.</em><br /> <em>死亡的时刻&#8230;到了&#8230;</em><br /></p> <div style="text-align: right;"> <p>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhi-zi-jiu-jun" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4326424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245628" alt="zhi_zi-jiu_jun" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4326424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhi-zi-jiu-jun" >zhi_zi-jiu_jun</a></span></p> </div> </blockquote> <blockquote> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span>留作纪念。</span></h2> </div> </blockquote> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-6" style="display:none"> <h1><span>Jan.</span></h1> <p><strong>SCPs：</strong></p> <p><strong>故事：</strong></p> <p><strong>GOI格式：</strong></p> <p><strong>图书馆：</strong></p> <p><strong>竞赛：</strong></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[征文排名I]</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">[Right&nbsp;Here]</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"></div> </div> </div> <hr /></div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-7" style="display:none"> <h1><span>结语：Nothing is sad until it's over.</span></h1> <hr /> <blockquote> <p>很高兴与各位相遇，欢迎加我的腾讯™QQ：<strong>1577299231</strong>找我聊天。</p> </blockquote> <p><strong>图书在版编目（CIP）数据</strong></p> <p>已有之事.—The Past：卡帕莱莫第七出版社，1519（1521.12重印）</p> <p>ISBN ISBN 978-7-1519-9541-8</p> <p>I.①已有… II.①漆析… III.①旅行游记—个人记录—“现在” IV.①G071</p> <p>Locus Orchard ver. 图书馆CIP数据核字（1519）第095217号<br /> <br /> <br /></p> <p><strong>已有之事</strong><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smith-sister-con" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4381648&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245628" alt="Smith_sister-con" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4381648)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smith-sister-con" >Smith_sister-con</a></span> 编</p> <hr /> <p><strong>责任编辑</strong> Vivejo</p> <p><strong>封面设计</strong> M