> - 出版物“<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:from-the-editor-s-desk">the Planasthai</a>”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%91%98" target="_blank">图书管理员</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/librarians" target="_blank">librarians</a>)</em></strong> - 实体“图书管理员”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%80%81%E8%A1%A8%E9%98%BF%E4%B8%B9" target="_blank">老表阿丹</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cousin-dan" target="_blank">cousin-dan</a>)</em></strong> - 人物“老表阿丹”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ulak" target="_blank">ulak</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ulak" target="_blank">ulak</a>)</em></strong> - 人物“漫游者Ulak”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%9B%BE%E4%B9%A6%E9%A6%86" target="_blank">图书馆</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/library" target="_blank">library</a>)</em></strong> - 与图书馆本身有关的文章。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/elrich" target="_blank">elrich</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/elrich" target="_blank">elrich</a>)</em></strong> - 地点或领域“Elrich”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/unwaking" target="_blank">unwaking</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/unwaking" target="_blank">unwaking</a>)</em></strong> - 世界或地点“the Unwaking”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/yoren" target="_blank">yoren</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/yoren" target="_blank">yoren</a>)</em></strong> - 世界或地点“Yoren”。</li> </ul> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-4" style="display:none"> <h2><span>特性标签</span></h2> <p>有关特定概念、构思或特性的标签。一篇文章可以有多个特性标签，也可以完全没有！</p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%B4%B5%E6%97%8F" target="_blank">贵族</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/aristocratic" target="_blank">aristocratic</a>)</em></strong> - 与皇室、贵族或类似阶层有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%A5%A5%E7%A7%98%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9" target="_blank">奥秘植物</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cryptobotanical" target="_blank">cryptobotanical</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种未曾被正式记载或者超自然的植物有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%A5%A5%E7%A7%98%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9" target="_blank">奥秘动物</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cryptozoological" target="_blank">cryptozoological</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种未曾被公开记载或者超自然的动物有关。请勿与“<strong>异界</strong>”混淆，后者代表通过密径连接的其他世界。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%A5%9E%E7%81%B5" target="_blank">神灵</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/divine" target="_blank">divine</a>)</em></strong> - 与神灵起源或能力相关的个体、物体或概念有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93" target="_blank">个体</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/entity" target="_blank">entity</a>)</em></strong> - 与一个超自然的独立个体有关，而不是表现得像一堆有机体的东西。能被“<strong>奥秘植物</strong>”或“<strong>奥秘动物</strong>”取代。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E4%B8%9B%E6%9E%97" target="_blank">丛林</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/forest" target="_blank">forest</a>)</em></strong> - 与特定丛林有关，或者发生于丛林的故事。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2" target="_blank">历史</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/historical" target="_blank">historical</a>)</em></strong> - 与知名的历史重要事件有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA" target="_blank">地区</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/location" target="_blank">location</a>)</em></strong> - 与一个具有特别意义的地理区域有关。已有“设定标签”的区域不再需要“<strong>地区</strong>”标签。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%86%9B%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">军队</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/military" target="_blank">military</a>)</em></strong> - 与一支军事力量或者该军事力量的某次行动——例如战争——有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%9D" target="_blank">神话</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/" target="_blank">mythological</a>)</em></strong> - 与现有的神话、传说或故事有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%93" target="_blank">物体</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/object" target="_blank">object</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种超自然或者具有重要现实意义的物体有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%BC%82%E7%95%8C" target="_blank">异界</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/otherworldly" target="_blank">otherworldly</a>)</em></strong> - 与一个或多个其他宇宙世界有关。注意图书馆本身并不能算是一个世界。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E6%80%A7" target="_blank">宗教性</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/religion" target="_blank">religion</a>)</em></strong> - 与某个特定的宗教及其习俗或信仰有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E4%BB%AA%E5%BC%8F" target="_blank">仪式</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ritual" target="_blank">ritual</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种由一个或多个有智力的团体所进行的仪式性且可靠的过程有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA" target="_blank">太空</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/space" target="_blank">space</a>)</em></strong> - 与被称作“太空”的真空空间有关。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E9%AC%BC%E7%81%B5" target="_blank">鬼灵</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/spirit" target="_blank">spirit</a>)</em></strong> - 与被称作“鬼灵”的个体有关，例如鬼魂、幽灵和恶魔。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD" target="_blank">部落</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/tribal" target="_blank">tribal</a>)</em></strong> - 与某种由人类或类人生物所组成的、部落形式的、有组织的社会团体。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%AF%86%E5%BE%84" target="_blank">密径</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ways" target="_blank">ways</a>)</em></strong> - 与一种被称之为“<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:the-universe#toc4">密径</a>”的现象有关。</li> </ul> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-5" style="display:none"> <h2><span>竞赛标签</span></h2> <p>用于官方竞赛的标签。</p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wlc2013" target="_blank">wlc2013</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wlc2013" target="_blank">wlc2013</a>)</em></strong> - <a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:first-annual-wanderer-s-library-writing-contest-ar">2013被放逐者之图书馆竞赛</a>。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%AB%9E%E8%B5%9B" target="_blank">生活竞赛</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/life-contest" target="_blank">life-contest</a>)</em></strong> - 首页征文“<a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:fictionalized-life-stories-contest">虚构的生活故事</a>”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wanderlust01" target="_blank">wanderlust01</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/wanderlust01" target="_blank">wanderlust01</a>)</em></strong> - 第一期首页征文“迷失”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/spacewitch02" target="_blank">spacewitch02</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/spacewitch02" target="_blank">spacewitch02</a>)</em></strong> - 第二期首页征文“太空巫师”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/relationship03" target="_blank">relationship03</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/relationship03" target="_blank">relationship03</a>)</em></strong> - 第三期首页征文“联系”。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/cities04" target="_blank">cities04</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/