 <div id="wiki-tab-0-6" style="display:none"> <h2><span>已归档的标签</span></h2> <p>这些标签曾用于图书馆，但由于种种原因现已归档、不再使用。<strong>这些标签不应该用于任何新创作的作品中。</strong></p> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/swedenborg" target="_blank">swedenborg</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/swedenborg" target="_blank">swedenborg</a>)</em></strong> - 伪斯韦登伯格（the False Swedenborg）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/pangur" target="_blank">pangur</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/pangur" target="_blank">pangur</a>)</em></strong> - 潘古尔（Pangur）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/redtooth" target="_blank">redtooth</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/redtooth" target="_blank">redtooth</a>)</em></strong> - 艾米莉·红齿（Emily Redtooth）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/thorn" target="_blank">thorn</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/thorn" target="_blank">thorn</a>)</em></strong> - 荆棘顽童（the Thorn Child）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ilvos" target="_blank">ilvos</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/ilvos" target="_blank">ilvos</a>)</em></strong> - 锈蚀骑士团的艾尔沃斯（Ilvos of the Rusted Blade）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/bogg" target="_blank">bogg</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/bogg" target="_blank">bogg</a>)</em></strong> - 阿格奈什·博格（Agnes Bogg）书架。</li> </ul> <ul> <li><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/kragg" target="_blank">kragg</a></strong> <strong><em>(<a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/kragg" target="_blank">kragg</a>)</em></strong> - 恐惧飞龙克拉（the Dread Wyrm Kragg）书架。</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1745583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610245634" alt="MScarlet" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1745583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" >MScarlet</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">脚注</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-779999-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. 部分语言分部仍使用“<strong>未分级</strong>”标签，注意在翻译时需要修改为“<strong>机密分级</strong>”。</div> </div> 
